data.description: HENRICO's NEWEST TOWNHOME COMMUNITY - GROVE POINT! Lots of living space and an abundance of natural light make the Beethoven a townhome that feels like a single-family home. On the main level, a huge Kitchen, with island and all SS Appliances, provides plenty of room for cooking and entertaining and opens to a large airy Living Room with a powder room. Upstairs are two spacious bedrooms with ample closet space, a hall bath, and a generous Owner’s Bedroom that features a huge walk-in closet. A separate Owner’s Bath features a 5’ shower. The Beethoven features a finished basement with a huge recreation room, with an option to add a study with french doors and another powder room. Enjoy hosting nights outdoor on your 10 x 10 patio.
